Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:23.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's happened since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's incredible\Nthat we survived at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:56.44,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7\NChagum's Resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See to it that Chagum's image\Nis engraved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect...\NYes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am well aware that only those\Nwho held the rank of mikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:08.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...are permitted to have their likeness\Nengraved in stone for perpetuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let them mock me as\Na foolish father. I care not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:19.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was Chagum's death that spared\Nthis country from the water demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:25.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If his noble sacrifice does not warrant\Nbeing remembered forever, what does?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:30.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sign of the great drought\Nshould lift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how things\Nturned out yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. For now, at least,\Nthere's nothing to be done about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just thankful to be\Nhere with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like noisy crowds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:57.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I find the vigor of the\Ncommon people most appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not at all unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, regular townsfolk\Ndon't speak like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:10.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's quite a hidden gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When can we move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:19.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can move in right away.\NAll that's left for you to do is pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the same, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told Toya and Saya everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:31.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were both pretty angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did cause\Na lot of trouble for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toya is anxious to come back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a townsman\Nthrough and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:03.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Balsa, the whole town\Nis full of gossip about you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one would ever guess that\Nthe subject of their gossip...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...would be sitting here having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Care to put it to the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of a bodyguard\Nwho goes by the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Balsa the Spear-wielder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's the talk of the town\Nat the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:40.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess,\Nyou're new in town, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:46.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so curious about her,\NI can tell you all that you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:51.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a dastardly villain\Nwho set fire to the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...killed the prince and then died in a\Nhuge battle against a thousand pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say! How incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:04.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damned right. But as someone\Nwho's crossed swords with her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to say her demise\Nwas rather anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! You mean you've\Nfought this Balsa person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! She may have\Nbeen a female bodyguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but she was more ferocious\Nthan any man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her spear attacks\Nwere so overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that even I could\Njust barely earn a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:27.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had always hoped to settle\Nthe score with her one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but now I'll never get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dish called "gisho."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gisho?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they serve a Yakoo man\Nwho won't be taking over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...as head of his family\Nto celebrate his having established...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a family of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:17.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Yakoo place a high value\Non celebrations like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These big fava beans\Nrepresent the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The red, slender beans\Nare the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:31.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the little yellow\Nchickpeas are the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:56.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no longer any need\Nto decipher the epistles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may return to\Nyour star reader duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How powerless I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How incompetent I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:16.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to accomplish\Nanything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking a bit of a shortcut,\Nso this is where we part company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:58.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should keep the wolves away,\Nbut be careful all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Off with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:33.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:48.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...if this was any of your previous jobs,\Nyou'd be done at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You would be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the bodyguard business...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the job is typically over once\Nyou've driven off your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we make a quick stop here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out of herbs\Nfor treating wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like some of my usual medicinal\Nherbs if you have them in stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting what I need\Nfrom his storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:14.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, are you sure you're up to\Nhandling things from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Handle what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking after someone\Nyour whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is basically the same\Nas being a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\NI suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been\Nan herbologist, Tanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:38.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I started mixing\Nmedicines when I was 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...using the reference guides\Nmy mentor made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you started working\Nat quite a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was the youngest child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had to learn self-reliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so that I'd be able to\Nearn my own living one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll catch up\Nwith you after I make...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a quick trip back and\Nbuy the rest of what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commoners cannot stay in their homes\Nunless they pay money to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get anything\Nif you don't pay for it with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the concept\Nof exchanging money for goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also understand\Npaying money for services...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...like when you were\Npaid money to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I paid money at the inn, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:48.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One pays money even to sleep?\NBut it was I who slept, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take a client's money\Nif I slept on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:55.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To a commoner, money rules\Nall aspects of life, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:04.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we've handed over all of\Nthe treasure given to us by Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can rest easy now. You seem like\Nan honest, upstanding family to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:29.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but the boy\Nis someone else's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due to various circumstances,\Nhe was left in our care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:39.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Taking in someone else's\Nchild is no trivial matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That speaks well of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will find this acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I might not live out the term\Nthat this much money will cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if my wife were still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:08.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't have to impose on\Nmy daughter and her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my useless rambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Jiguro felt\Nwhen he was in this position?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose when you're\Nraised by a man of few words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you grow up to be\Na silent person yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't do, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:09.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the house that we\Nwill be living in from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to take up\Nresidence here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've guessed one would\Npay in gold coins to live in a water mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hidden gem, that's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we give it a try?\NWho knows, it might be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to operate\Na waterwheel, Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:32.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. isn't it nice to be living in\Na house that has devices like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:36.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think the roof might need\Nto be thatched again, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I expect that will cost money too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bought too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bought too much.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to treat you two to a fine meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and by the time I'd bought\Neverything, it had gotten late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be ready in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, do you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am in good health thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been through quite an ordeal\Nover these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no harm in filling yourself up\Nwith a hearty meal for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that I wish\Nto discuss with the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for all that\Nyou have done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this earring\Nas a token of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a debt of gratitude that\NI shall never forget as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:29.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot bring myself to\Nimpose on you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided that from\Ntoday forward, I shall fend for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd been acting funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So is that what you've\Nbeen brooding over all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You find this amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:05.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, how would you\Nsupport yourself if you left us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It may not be as extensive as Tanda's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have knowledge of\Nmedicines and animals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will get by somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You silly boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:25.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I met your mother,\Nthat's what I promised her, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, there are\Nlots of people in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:34.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who wouldn't turn away a boy like you\Neven if they weren't paid to take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:40.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But money is needed\Nto survive, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:47.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's no need for you\Nto give that a moment's thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sign of the great drought\Nhas not disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:43.91,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:44.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A visit is paid to Balsa's\Nlongstanding blacksmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:46.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There they are reunited...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:49.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...with someone unexpected.\NSomeone other than the blacksmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:52.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"The Swordsmith."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8\NThe Swordsmith
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.89,0:24:55.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that qualifies one...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.09,0:24:57.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to wield the ultimate blade?
